CAPUT VIII.


Introducta timet pia virgo, propheta [3 1Kb] timoris.
   Supplicat in vultu simpliciore rubor.
Illibata timet fossorem gleba, timescit
   Ad maris accessum virginitatis honor.
Angelici monitus Tobias fit memor, inde
   Cassiduli [4 1Kb] profert auxiliare jecur.
Servati jecoris partem carbone marito [5 1Kb]
   Urit, odor fumi spargitur, hostis abest [6 1Kb] ,
